---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DarkHeader from '../../components/DarkHeader.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Bikes Bikes Bikes — Cooper Minehart"
  description="Bikes Bikes Bikes."
>
  <DarkHeader>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-10">
      <a href="/hobbies" class="text-sm text-forest-400 hover:text-forest-300 mb-6 inline-block">← Hobbies</a>
      <p class="section-label-light mb-3">Hobbies</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-white">Bikes Bikes Bikes</h1>
    </div>
  </DarkHeader>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-10 pb-24">
    <div class="text-[#333] leading-relaxed mb-14">
      <p class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-1">TEN-O-CYCLE</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#888] italic mb-6">by Shel Silverstein</p>
      <p class="whitespace-pre-line">You pedal, you pump,
You bump on your rump,
You're sweatin' and ready to cuss,
When you're ridin' a bicycle built for ten
(And the other nine took the bus).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12">

      <div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg aspect-[4/3] bg-stone-100 mb-4">
          <img src="/photos/bike-dog.jpeg" alt="Riding the cargo bike with Yodi" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#555]">
          Cargo bike with Yodi. He was very happy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg aspect-[4/3] bg-stone-100 mb-4">
          <img src="/photos/homies-on-bikes.jpeg" alt="Homies before the Tour de Los Padres bikepacking race" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#555]">
          Pre-race photo before the Tour de Los Padres. A bikepacking race through the Los Padres
          National Forest,a lot of climbing, a lot of hike-a-bike, and more hallucinating than
          I expected.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg aspect-[4/3] bg-stone-100 mb-4">
          <img src="/photos/bike-surf.jpeg" alt="Riding to Morro Bay with a longboard" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#555]">
          Rode to Morro Bay with the longboard strapped to the bike.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg aspect-[4/3] bg-stone-100 mb-4">
          <img src="/photos/walter-puffy-bikepacking.jpeg" alt="Walt and Cooper camping on the grade" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#555]">
          Walt and I camping on the grade. Always pack a hammer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg aspect-[4/3] bg-stone-100 mb-4">
          <video src="/photos/santa-barbara-snowing.mov" autoplay muted loop playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover"></video>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#555]">
          Biking from the 166 to Ventura, ran into a snow storm on Pine Canyon. Very wet. I'm a weak west coaster now.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
